Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:16.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All I can say is\Nwhat we have is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:18.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you forsaking our love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:34.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you, Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:55.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It was an old movie, but I know why\NMeimi's parents recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:57.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:01.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Gee, how I hope I find\Na love like that one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:07.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He kinda looked like Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out and find us\Nsome fantastic boyfriends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:17.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:27.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Platform of Love and Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And how was the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It was so touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It was a true love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They fall in love\Ndespite their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, they part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The actor who played\NJoseph was so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How sickening.\NWhat's all this mush about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How dare you eavesdrop on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:06.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why do girls always get so excited\Nwhen they talk about love and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand\Nabout true love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:14.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All you ever think\Nabout is St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You've traveled all of\NJapan on a bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:46.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I met Minako here in this city\Non the last leg of my trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But then his bicycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not really, if you\Nhave the determination...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,you could do it as well, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Since you live in Japan,\Nyou can try it anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I'll give it try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm really glad I got to\Nmeet someone nice like you, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've met a lot of people along\Nthe way but none so nice as...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please open this gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:15.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:19.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is all the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Madame, these people\Nare demanding to be let in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A boy took John's bike\Nand went into the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:34.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's why we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you accusing\Nmy son Tatsuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:46.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo has a first class American\Nbicycle, ordered especially for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My name is on that bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:51.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any more of\Nyour ridiculous accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We went back several times,\Nbut no one would listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And since it concerns a child, John\Ndoesn't want the police involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:14.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That bike was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'd been through good times\Nand bad times on our travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:23.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait for the boy to\Nreturn the bicycle on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:27.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure our prayers\Nwill be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John and Minako.\NThey're in love, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Such a dramatic meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:45.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And their love will burn furiously,\Nonly to end in a sad parting of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright.\NI'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Only we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:06:00.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John is returning to America\Non the last flight this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We have to get it back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can\Nin honor of their love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Dad is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He insists on eating Oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is my favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll put a lot in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"I will be at the Ninomiya residence\Ntonight to retrieve a bicycle."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How'd she know\Nthis was my favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, it's time for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yum. We're having Oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There, Ruby's aerial\Nmerry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can use it\Nin your next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Would you like\Nto be part of my show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And where's the bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if that\Nbike gets stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it\Nsupposed to be special?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:35.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,we should have given it\Nto that bothersome American.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? Yeah that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now, why would St. Tail\Nwant to steal this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Lord forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:19.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In order for John\Nto make his flight tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,he must take the train by 9 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,9 pm at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May God's blessings be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:36.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I want this room and\Nthe house closely guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Taking what is not\Nyours is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It was so cool,\NI couldn't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So you stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you're forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now for the real Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Somebody go check the fuse box!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A bicycle that flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll let the wind carry me\Nright to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?! You're not going to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Bring the patrol car around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I have an extra\Nballoon here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away\Nthis time, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:56.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, I've got to\Nput Asuka Jr. down somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I need to borrow your bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... it's 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:51.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's that kid's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Phew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I've got to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's... the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't, John. It will\Njust make things harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John... so that means\Nit was his bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:33.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get my bike back,\Nbut I'm glad I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's yours John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But who brought it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Our prayers were answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John, we'll meet again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never see\Nmy bike again, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So I know you\Nand I will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:05.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou look so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:52.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't hurt you\Nto talk about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph. It's only love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:01.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so Asuka Jr. is\Nin love with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:07.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
